#: templates/admin/admin_settings.php:44
msgid "The Gutenberg blocks require a bookable_id parameter."
msgstr "Gutenberg blocken kräver en bookable_id parameter."

#: templates/admin/admin_settings.php:46
msgid ""
"The calendar block will display a booking calendar. The available attribute "
"is <code>bookable_id</code> which is the MyClub Bookable item id."
msgstr ""
"Kalenderblocket visar en bokningskalender. Det tillgängliga attributet är "
"<code>bookable_id</code> vilket är MyClubs bokningsbara objekt ID."

#: templates/admin/admin_settings.php:51
msgid "Here are the shortcodes available from the MyClub booking plugin"
msgstr "Here are the shortcodes available from the MyClub booking plugin"

#: templates/admin/admin_settings.php:52
msgid ""
"The shortcode requires a bookable_id parameter. The bookable_id parameter "
"can be found in the table below - the bookable_id parameter is required."
msgstr ""
"Kortkoden kräver en bookable_id-parameter. Parametern bookable_id finns i "
"tabellen nedan - parametern bookable_id är obligatorisk."

#: templates/admin/admin_settings.php:54
msgid ""
"The calendar shortcode will display a booking calendar. The available "
"attributes are <code>bookable_id</code> which is the MyClub bookable id. "
"This is required."
msgstr ""
"Kalendern kortkoden visar en bokningskalender. De tillgängliga attributen är "
"<code>bookable_id</code> vilket är MyClubs bokningsbara ID. Detta är "
"obligatoriskt."

